        pricing_overview: '<p>Spellbook operates strictly as an Enterprise Legal SaaS provider. Pricing is opaque and heavily scaled based on the size of the law firm or legal department. It is an immense, high-ticket corporate expense justified entirely by the vast increase in "billable hour" efficiency of the attorneys utilizing the software, requiring massive security audits prior to enterprise deployment.</p>',
