            { group: 'Ecosystem & Organization', items: ['Long-form native distraction-free text editor', 'Canvas (Visual storyboarding and character mapping UI)', 'Deep context memory (remembers the "Story Bible" rules)', 'Multi-model routing (switching between Claude/OpenAI based on task)'] }
