        pros: ['The absolute, uncompromising dedication to *Narrative Fiction*; every single button, dropdown, and feature is mathematically optimized to help a human tell a story, making it utterly useless for corporate marketing but a god-send for artists', 'The "Story Engine" feature is a staggering architectural achievement, solving the classic AI problem where an LLM "forgets" who a character is by chapter 3 by utilizing a strict, continuously referenced internal Story Bible', 'Providing users the ability to seamlessly switch the backend underlying AI models (e.g., using an Anthropic Claude model for highly emotive dialogue, and an OpenAI model for aggressive action) grants unprecedented creative control', 'The UI is visually beautiful, calming, and drastically mitigates the high anxiety associated with the terrifying "blank page" syndrome'],
