        pricing_overview: '<p>Superhuman is the absolute poster-child for extreme Premium Productivity SaaS pricing. It refuses to offer a Free tier. It charges a high, flat monthly fee (often $30/mo) strictly for individual users. The pricing is entirely psychological: it filters out casual users and ensures that only elite professionals who fundamentally believe their saved time is mathematically worth hundreds of dollars an hour utilize the platform.</p>',
